answer: The study of the 5 Hz quasi-periodic oscillation in GRS 1739-278 extends our understanding of low-frequency QPOs and motivates further research on their properties in black-hole candidates (astro-ph/0104421).
explanation: This paper presents a detailed study of the 5 Hz QPO in GRS 1739-278, providing insights into the properties of low-frequency QPOs in black-hole candidates.
